message:
Add NPM script for starting Gulp (#32)

* Add NPM script for starting Gulp

Typing `gulp` in the terminal will not start the gulp server unless it's installed globally. The NPM script enables a local install of gulp to be run by running `npm run gulp`.

* Updated README

Updated README with instructions to run the gulp server using NPM scripts.

Migrate from HTML to Pug. (#64)

* Migrate from HTML to Jade.

* Replace jade with pug and fix HTMLs.

* Remove jsdom from deps.

* Update image paths.

* Update packages.

* dist.
Merge branch 'dev' of github.com:froala/design-blocks into dev
